title: 03/16/21 DPS Hour 3 Shaq Barrett and Sean Payton
itunes:title: 03/16/21 DPS Hour 3 Shaq Barrett and Sean Payton
description:
Shaq Barrett tells Dan what it was like to win a Superbowl with Tom Brady. Shaq says he still would not name his son Brady though. Sean Payton talks to Dan about prior drafts. Sean tells Dan that they are set at the QB for right now.
